40:42.701 --> 40:44.093
YOU MADE A FRIEND?

40:44.659 --> 40:45.965
I'M SO PROUD OF YOU.

40:46.095 --> 40:47.314
[VOCALISES]

40:50.056 --> 40:51.536
TELL HER WHOSE IN THE PICTURE,
TIMMY.

40:53.755 --> 40:55.017
MOMMY.

40:56.976 --> 40:58.543
[GASPS]

41:00.806 --> 41:02.460
[JOYFUL GASPS]

41:15.298 --> 41:16.430
MOMMY.

41:23.437 --> 41:24.612
WOW.

41:25.570 --> 41:27.136
SOUNDS LIKE YOU HAD
AN INCREDIBLE TRIP.

41:27.920 --> 41:30.357
IT WAS UNBELIEVABLE,
JUST LIKE YOU SAID.

41:32.272 --> 41:33.665
[JOYFUL LAUGHS]

41:44.545 --> 41:46.721
[END THEME PLAYING]
